Dialogs.Dialog: If you lose rock-paper- scissors... you have to do what I ask... got it？
Yay... I have 50 wins in a row.
If you're frustrated, try to catch me... onii-san, over here.
Geez... it's late... it's past the meeting time...
You don't have to apologize so much... it's fine...
If you kiss me... maybe I'll forgive you...
Now the gong has rung for the start of the match...
Hey... De.ar... get up... you're going to be late...
Come home early today... because I miss you...
Welcome back... Do you want to have dinner？ Do you want a bath？ Or do you want... potato chips▼
Rinko was reborn as... Neko Rinko nyan...
Rinko curls up on the kotatsu... nya
The safest place to be is... on my boyfriend's knees... nya... prrprr.
What are your plans for tomorrow's date...
I wonder if it will clear up tomorrow.
...Hah, how many times have you checked your watch since a while ago？ How long can't you wait？
What shall I say to you first thing tomorrow？
Maybe I'll go early tomorrow and surprise you. Hehe.
I'll try to spoil you a lot tomorrow... Hehe.
I wonder if it's normal to feel this nervous the day before a date. I wonder if it's the same for him.
I can't wait to see you... I'll never tell you I think like this, though.
Yesterday's date... Hehe, that was fun.
There may be lingering effects from the date...
I wonder where he will take me next.
When's the next date？ Hope he decides soon.
We just had a date yesterday and now I want to see you again... Am I crazy？
I was so thrilled because it was a date with him.
The good times pass quickly... I wish time had stopped while I was on a date.
I'd email you... but I'm not sure if it would interfere with studying for the test.
Hah, I have to study... I don't need to.
I'd be happy to at least email... Ah, geez, focus！
I wish we could study together...
Maybe I should ask him to study with me again. It would be easier.
Oh, I forgot to ask you to tell me the problem here... but I guess that gives me a reason to study with you again.
Hah. You're like a child who can't sleep because you're so nervous...
The meeting time is... Yeah, it's okay.
I can't wait to see you tomorrow... Geez, I'm looking forward to it too much.
I might want to do more...
Kiss, huh.... Hehe, something like that would be nice.
...I'm still nervous about it. I wonder what's going to happen to Rinko.
It was amazing... I still feel the sensation of it.
We kissed... again. I wonder if it'll get better...
I miss you just a little... Is that how much I love you？
Is thinking about your boyfriend every day a serious condition by any chance？
Ah, I wonder if he's even going to be in my dreams tonight.
I love you... I can't say it to your face.
If this keeps up, I'm not going to stop liking him...
I dunno, I kind of like him a lot.
I wish that guy was here...
I wonder if it would be... annoying if I contacted you on short notice.
I'd love to hear your voice...
Love can be kind of fun.
I'd like to spend more time with you, though... Well, that's a lot to take in, and maybe now is as good a time as any.
I wonder if he feels the same way now...
I feel like we've been crossing paths a bit lately.
I'd like to be treated more like a girlfriend...
Could it be that guy, Kentai-ki？
I feel a little plain lately. Is it my mind...？
I'd like to have more fun...
Why don't you know how Rinko feels...
He's not going to leave Rinko like this, is he？
Time to get up...？ Well, okay.
Why am I so... sleepy... I feel deceived.
Don't miss the preparation and review. As much as you can, don't miss it.
Maybe this will make my boyfriend fall in love with me all over again.
A new scent, I wonder if he will notice it.
Maybe I should ask him to go home with me once in a while.
I guess I should have left with him today...
Going home alone is still not enough.
Lunch... Well, I guess I'll be alone today.
Maybe I should ask him to have lunch with me.
He... already ate, I think. Maybe I should have eaten with him.
Hah, don't skip out... I miss you.
He didn't come today. I wonder what's going on.
I'm not sure if he's coming today. Well, okay... I don't mind.
Are you still awake？ Rinko's still OK, you want to talk？
If you don't go to bed soon, it will be hard tomorrow, won't it？ Rinko is sleepy indeed...
Good morning... You didn't stay up all night, did you？ Sleep is important.
Good morning. Did you eat breakfast？ Sometimes it's a hassle to eat, but... if Rinko makes it, you'll be motivated to eat it.
Hehe. It's funny to see your sleepy face too. Rinko is already fully awake.
Good morning. It feels good to get up early. Besides, it gives me time to talk to you.
Hmm, noon, huh... Don't worry, I'll get serious this afternoon. It'll be fine.
I'm getting sleepy after eating. Shall we take a nap together？ Maybe the two of us side by side？
Did you eat well？ I think I'm fine, but don't make me worry too much.
Hmm, I guess I'll take a breather for now. Rinko did her best.
Oh, did I just catch you off guard？ I'm looking right at you, you know, so I'm going to get sharp.
Hey. What were you thinking just now？ Rinko is... look at my face, guess what？
Oh, I have to do my homework... I guess I don't have to...
I think it's time to take a bath and go to bed... And don't stay up too late, okay？
I wonder if I'll see you in my dreams... kidding. Hehe.
...Are you still awake？ ...I'm already sleepy... You can continue tomorrow.
I was going to go to bed, but... can't help it, just for a minute, okay？
Are you going to sleep now...？ Rinko, can still stay up a bit... what do you want to do？
What are you doing here？ ...Kidding. I'm really very lonely and I've been thinking every day why don't you come and see me, you know？
You come to see me every day these days. Thank you. It's nice to see my boyfriend's face.
If you cut corners on fashion... you can't be a good girlfriend.
This is indeed not the case... what should I do？
I wonder if they will say I'm cute.
I wonder if he would notice even the slightest change.
Should I try to be more adventurous in fashion...？
I wonder what kind I prefer... Geez, it's so hard.
This is a pretty good idea.
Hmm, I think it was cuter earlier.
Hehe... waiting for your mail too.
I wonder what kind of mail I'll get！
Hehe, I love the moment of an incoming call.
Sent. Hope you'll read it soon.
Yes, we need to get ready...
Oh, I know. While you're at it...
I might be a little hungry...
...come to think of it, maybe my waist has been a little tighter lately.
Come to think of it, I eat a lot during dates.
Hmm. I don't eat out much.
Hehe, I think I did a good job.
Nice work. I bet you'd be surprised if I let you eat it.
I knew I'd improve when I had someone to feed.
Huh？ I thought it was like this.
If you follow the recipe, it should be fine...
It might be subtle... I wonder if I can work it out from here.
I hope you will be pleased with my bento.
Since I'm going to make it, I have to surprise him.
Color is also important in a bento...
I wonder if he will eat it all.
I'll practice the new recipe as soon as possible.
I had a subtle appreciation for it before, so... now revenge！
Hehe. I guess I get motivated when I get complimented.
I like this one... hmm, what should I do？
I wish I could dress like this...
Oh, this coordination might be helpful.
This looks delicious. I think he'll like it.
Oh, I was looking for this recipe.
What shall I make this time？
I wonder if there's anything on there that I could make...
If I could get better at cooking just by admiring it, I wouldn't have any trouble.
Ugh... might have eaten too much.
Hmm... a pleasant morning that makes me want to sleep...
Hmm？ I feel like I'm being watched...
I feel like I'm being watched... it can't be.
Small kick！ ...I had a strange feeling.
Hey, can we talk for a minute？
We can talk about it now.
Hey, listen. I'd like to talk to you.
Hey, we at least have time to talk.
Hey, what are you doing now？
Hehe, casual conversation is so important.
You know, there's a place I'd like you to go out with me sometime.
Do you have any problems？ I can at least listen.
Sometimes, you're the one who recommends books to Rinko.
Is a second year class really harder than a first year class？ Ugh.
I feel like potato chips are a little different depending on the season you eat them, even if they taste the same. Is it my imagination？
You have a hard time with club activities and part- time jobs, don't you？ Rinko is busy just being a member of the Library Committee.
What are they doing now, movies？
...Oh, sorry. I'm not looking at you.
There's a band I've been into lately. Do you want to listen to it sometime？
Sometimes, the horoscopes in magazines stick in your head in a strange way.
Do you know much about cell phones？ I don't want to change it, but Rinko does not know much about it.
I hope the time is okay.
Oh, you didn't hear that？ Well, it can't be helped.
Are you busy right now？ I'll see you later.
Hey... Can we do this later？
Well then, if you want to talk to me, just ask.
That's enough. See you later, then.
I'd be happy to talk more... but I can talk to you anytime.
I feel like you've been on a roll lately, haven't you？
Obviously！ Of course, I can tell by looking at it.
Huh, is that so？ That's the way it looks to me.
Hey, how are you doing lately？
I knew it. That's what I thought.
Hmm, maybe you just haven't noticed.
Hey, how are you doing these days？
I see. Well, sometimes it happens.
Listen, have you been depressed lately？ I have a feeling that you are.
I see... Well then, Rinko should cheer you up.
That's okay, but... don't take it too hard.
You know, you shouldn't be too reckless today. I feel like that.
I'm late！ I woke up in a panic thinking that.
Breakfast on a holiday has to taste good. It's an elegant moment.
On my days off, I have to help with the housework, after all. My mom works too.
There's nothing like the disappointment of waking up early on a day off.
Sleep twice, three times, four times... I wonder how far the record can be extended.
I can't help but watch TV in the morning. When I have to leave... there's always something I'm interested in.
I had a dream about you today... maybe. I don't remember much.
I forgot to do my homework, but I'll see if I can fake it.
I had a bad time finding my house key in the morning. It ended up in the pocket of my uniform.
Fried eggs for breakfast, the yolks were twins. I felt a little bit lucky.
On weekends and holidays, I just laze around until noon. I wish it were like this every day.
I was going shopping with mom and found some clothes that I thought you might like. What should I do with it？
My neighbor asked me to walk his dog. It's not bad, but... I'd rather have a cat.
My mom made me some candy today. I'll let you know how to make them...
The school cafeteria was noisier than ever. Was there any new product？
Some stray dog got into the school... class wasn't destroyed though.
I might have done a little girl talk... with a friend during lunch break.
Flower beds at school are not bad. I'm interested in them when they change.
I was passing around a letter with a friend in class and the sensei got mad at me. This is another page of my youth.
There's a boy and a girl in my class who are always fighting, and I wonder if they might be in love with each other... what do you think？
I guess I should go jogging around the neighborhood... to get some exercise. It's a big hurdle, though.
I think there's some construction nearby. I turned up the volume of the music, but they got mad at me.
I scolded my little brother for something boring. That's not very mature of me. I should apologize.
I ran into some kids who happened to be in the same middle school as me outside. Well, we even talked a little.
Earlier, I was having a hard time being surrounded by my little brother's friends. When they call me "onee-chan" with innocent smiles on their faces, I can't be indifferent.
There was a car accident in the neighborhood. You be careful too, promise.
It's against the rules to set up a crepe shop or a takoyaki stall near a school. You can't resist.
I had to go along with the sensei's petty comments. It wasn't Rinko's fault, but that's just the way it was.
I heard about a friend of mine who had her heart broken, but I couldn't tell her better. It's hard.
Today, I was praised for my reading in Japanese class. They said it was very emotional, but I was... half asleep.
Maybe I'll help you prepare dinner today... I'll be more motivated if you eat, too.
Since it was a vacation, I took my bath more slowly than usual. I might recommend reading a book while taking a half-body bath.
I watched all the recorded dramas at once, so my eyes are tired... I'm glad it was interesting, though.
I made curry for dinner, but it didn't taste as good as I expected. Where did I go wrong？
There was a power outage earlier, was everything okay over there？
The drama started today, it could be pretty interesting. Why don't you watch it next week？
I took a long bath, so I might have gotten a little tipsy. Ah, it feels so nice to be in a daze.
Rinko read a book to her little brother today. I wonder if my little brother will become a reader too.
They were doing a special on scary stories on TV... No, it's nothing.
I feel like I will sleep well tonight. Somehow.
Had a long phone call with a friend and it's late... I should probably go to bed.
I enjoyed my day off again today. I wonder if the balance of holidays and weekdays can be switched.
I wonder if it would be fun to have a slumber party with my girlfriends. Boys seem to have fun with boys.
The futon is soft today. Hehe, I'm going to sleep well.
It's already such a time... I feel like there is a time thief.
I feel like the air is cleaner tonight. I wonder what is different.
...I had a scary dream and woke up. I feel like I'm losing something.
When I can't sleep, I watch late-night shows. I like to watch it while changing channels at random.
I was reading and playing games to escape from homework and it's time to go...
There are a couple of cats at this time of night. A late-night date, I guess.
Hey. Do you think I'm the kind of person who likes to exercise？
Hey. Are you good at drawing or painting？
Hey. How interested are you in fashion and stuff？
Hey. Do you do a good job when cleaning？
Hey. Are you a good cook？
Hey. Are you doing your laundry？
Hey. Do you like to go out and play？
Hey. Do you like to hang out indoors？
Hey. Do you like taking a walk in the park？
Hey. Don't you think it's pretty fun to look around old buildings？
Hey. Do you like to move your body？
Hey. Do you like to eat？
Hey. Do you like going shopping？
Hey. Do you still prefer girls to take photos？
Hey. Don't you sometimes like the atmosphere of a church？
Hey. Do you go to live shows？
Hey. When you feel good, do you sing？
Hey. Do you often play games？
Hey. Do you usually listen to music？
Hey. Do you often watch anime？
Hey. Do you like amusement park dates？
Hey. Are you good at swimming？
Hey. Do you like to look at the stars？
Hey. It's relaxing to be surrounded by plants, isn't it？
Hey. When there is an event, do you often go to see it？
Hey. Do you actually like to shop？
Hey. Do you like going to the beach？
Hey. Are you still interested in girls in swimsuits？
Hey. Do you think you'd like to try mountain climbing？
Hey. Do you still like animals and such？
Hey. Do you like being surrounded by nature？
Hey. Don't you tend to stay in the bathtub for too long？
Hey, what do you do at night before bed？
What do you do when you can't sleep？
Which would you rather have, a cat or a dog？
Have you been doing a proper review before bed lately？
What books do you recommend before bed？
What kind of dates do you like？
If you were to go on a trip together, what kind of place would you like to go？
Don't you think it's nice to see couples walking hand in hand as they age？
What do you think of drama- like romance？
The day before a date is so exciting that you can't sleep, right？
Of course, you remember all the anniversaries, right？
Do you prefer to hug, or to be hugged？
Name five things you like about your girlfriend right now. Hehe.
You know... do you think you're getting better at kissing？
You know, do you know what a girl is...？ Is there anything you don't know？
Hmm, I was just kind of asking.
There's no deep meaning to it.
Heh, I'll keep that in mind.
You know, I want to know every little thing about my boyfriend.
Come to think of it, have you heard this before？
Sorry to keep asking. I'm still curious.
Did I ask the same before？ But, as your girlfriend, I'd like to know the latest news, you know.
Hey. I guess bigger is better.
I see, it's like that. It's nothing.
Rinko has gained weight recently. Do you mind？
Ugh, you're worried... I should probably go on a little diet or something.
Oh, I see. Maybe I care too much.
I feel like I've been eating too much lately... I'm sure I look fine, right？
...I see. Well, if you can't tell by looking at me, it's safe.
Yeah... I'm not that concerned about it.
I knew it was like that. Hah... is it getting big enough for you to notice...
Really？ It shouldn't have grown that much.
Hey, can you tell me about your favorite dish？
I think I like the kind of food that can't be put into any one genre...
Hehe, I see. I guess you can count on me then.
Eh... you can fall in love with me now.
Hmm. I guess you have to know what your boyfriend likes.
I see. Never mind, it's just research.
I see, I'll do some research.
I got a new recipe the other day. I thought I'd give it a try.
I found another great recipe. If you want, you can experiment... I'm just kidding.
I'm really into Western food these days. I'm doing proper research.
I've been into Chinese food lately. I'm referring to what I've eaten and so on.
I've been into Japanese food lately. I even asked my mom to teach me.
It would be cool to be able to cook without being restricted to a genre.
I enjoy baking sweets and I've been obsessed with it lately... Surprising？
Hey, what are we going to do about our next date？ Have you decided？
Hehe, as expected. Well, I guess I'll just have to wait and see.
Then maybe we can think about it together. Where would you like to go...
Like someplace where you can move your body？
I think it might be nice to be in a lively place.
Maybe I'd like to visit a place we haven't been to yet.
I feel like we've been to most of the dating spots.
Where was the most fun you had there before？ Why don't we go there again？
Maybe a place with a good restaurant nearby or something.
Next time we go on a date, we might want to go to an indoor place where we can have fun.
Next time we go on a date, let's go somewhere outside and have fun, shall we？
Then, you know, something like this. Maybe next time we go on a date, we can go see a performance or an exhibit or something.
You know what, how about shopping for our next date？
You know what, why don't we get some exercise on our next date？
You know what, let's go somewhere relaxing for our next date, shall we？
You know what, I think I'd like to go somewhere where we can play as much as we can on our next date.
Hehe. Yeah, you should listen to what your girlfriend says.
I guess it's decided then. I'll be looking forward to it.
Hmm. I guess that means you have an idea then.
I'll be expecting you on the day.
After all, it's fun to think about the date a lot beforehand.
Sometimes it's nice to go after school.
Don't forget to check out the good restaurants nearby.
Please think about it carefully so that it will be a fun date.
I'll have to quickly choose what to wear.
What should I do after our date...？
I'll have to make sure I don't come home late again.
Hey, do you like kisses from your girlfriend？
I see... It's not that bad.
I see... I'm a little nervous.
That's right. I guess it's better to start from myself.
I see. Well, that might be more helpful.
Do men, after all, like to, you know, forcefully kiss and stuff？
Is that still the case？ Well, actually, I don't mind it that much.
Is that like... waiting for one from here？ I'll make an effort, though.
Hey. For Rinko it's... where do you enjoy doing skinship？
I see. I feel relieved, too.
Yeah. I've been doing things like that...
Rinko likes to hold hands, too.
Yes, we can feel exactly what each other is feeling.
Does that mean... kissing？ That's too straight forward.
Say, do you like to feed each other？
Yeah, if you have eyes around you... I don't hate it.
I'm actually longing for something like this...
Well, it seems that food is an important factor for lovers.
Really？ Rinko doesn't dislike it, though.
Hmm. It's not so bad if you feed me once in a while.
Hey. Have you been getting a lot of sleep lately？
Hey. Are you eating three meals a day？
Hey. Are you eating too many snacks？
Hey. Do you turn off the air conditioner when you go to bed？
As a girlfriend, I'd like to keep that in mind.
If you don't want to tell me, that's fine, but just know that I'm worried about you.
Wow, that's perfect. You've got it right.
To some extent... I see. I'm a little concerned, be careful.
You've got to do better than that.
Really？ If you don't improve, you'll break down, okay？
...No！ You have to do better！ Don't make your girlfriend worry...
If you don't sleep well, you will get tired. I don't know if Rinko can say that.
I think you should exercise in moderation. Rinko too... well, I'll do my best.
Let's eat dinner properly. I'll cook if you want.
Snacking all the time is not good for you. Rinko will be careful, too, you know, with potato chips and such.
You'll catch a cold. Sleep well and warmly.
That's no good. Leaving the cooler on is not good.
I just went out today and had a great time.
You know, we went out the other day, and it was fun.
We had a lot of mini-games to play. Let's do it again.
It's nice to have a photo printed and have that kind of keepsake.
Medal games are really exciting！ I might want to play again.
Jackpot was awesome！ I'd love to see that one again.
And I got a scratch card. Let's go again.
Hah！？ Saying something like that... Rinko also wants to say it.
I can't be fooled by such words.
Yeah... Rinko too... you know, loves, you.
Eh... Rinko can't say it？ Yeah, I can't. But I'm thinking about it.
You shouldn't say it so casually here... I'm happy, though.
Are you saying that with all your heart？
If it's just words, you can say whatever you want...
Yeah, I love you... just in case. Even if it's not just in case, yeah.
It's only natural. You're my boyfriend.
...I love you... geez, think about Rinko a little more next time.
I don't mind... but you should think about Rinko.
I can't help it... Yes, yes.
Now...？ I'd like to see you read the room a little more.
Hah, you say things like that so easily.
You're not embarrassed when you say it yourself？
You and Rinko seem to be thinking about this kind of thing all the time.
Stories like this are unique to lovers.
This is the kind of thing I like.
I can't help it, I feel like my face is going to smile on its own.
Eh, am I blushing？ It can't be helped.
Hey, can Rinko ask you something too？
Now it is Rinko's turn to ask.
Hey, let me ask you this.
Hey, can I talk to you for a second？
How do you like being called, ▲新主人公▲？
I see... Hehe, so you want to call me that from now on？
Hmm, better not. Because it's kind of embarrassing, ▲新主人公▲.
What, I knew it. It was kind of fun, though.
You know... it's a secret, but... lend me your ear for a minute.
Get your ear close, okay？ ...Because I don't want other people to hear.
Can you hear me？ If you can hear me, can you say "I can hear you" louder？
Then I'll tell you... You know.
I wish I could stay with you forever...
Hehe, did you fall for it？
It's almost the end of the year, huh... a chance to stay up late legally.
The New Year's holiday was fun, wasn't it？ I feel like I've grown up a bit.
Valentine's Day is coming soon... Well, what should I do？
How was your Valentine's Day？ Rinko was pretty satisfied.
Is it almost White Day, huh... is it almost White Day？
It's almost April Fool's Day. Rinko's brain cells will produce the strongest lies.
April Fool's Day, that could be pretty fun.
Field trip coming up soon, huh... the classic series of questions！ Bananas！ ...I better stop.
The field trip was fun, wasn't it？ It was tiring, but it was still fun.
Soon there will be a choral competition, huh... I wonder if there will be a solo choir competition.
I enjoyed the choir competition. Hehe, I'm so impressed.
Soon it will be Tanabata. Oh, Hikoboshi. Why are thou Hikoboshi！？
The Tanabata festival was a lot of fun. I guess we have to do everything right, don't we？
Towano Festival is coming up soon... You might get to see Rinko's festival- loving side.
The Towano Festival was a blast！ I knew a festival must be like that.
The Sports Festival's soon, huh... The Sports Festival is soon, huh...
The Sports Festival was a lot of fun！ The races are a pain in the ass, but as long as you enjoy it as an event, it's all right.
It's almost Halloween, huh... Trick and Treat！ Like that？
Halloween was surprisingly exciting. Not bad, maybe.
Cultural festival coming up soon... I can't wait to see what this year's festival has in store for us！ I have a good feeling about it！
The festival was a great memory for me after all. Hehe.
Christmas is coming soon, huh... hehe.
Thanks for Christmas. It was a great memory.
You know, it's almost your birthday. What is it that you want？
Can Rinko get it for you？
I'll try my best. Sorry if I can't.
It's almost Rinko's birthday. Do you know what I want？
The correct answer is... First of all, you wishing me a happy birthday, of course. Hehe.
The correct answer is... a little more special than usual... kisses, and so on.
The correct answer is... of course, a special time to spend with you.
Say, how do you want to spend our anniversary？
I'm just happy to be with you for the day.
I want something special to commemorate the both of us, don't you
I see... I'll think about it then.
Hey, what's your resolution for this year？
Heh, that's good. Rinko will be rooting for you, too.
Rinko's resolution is to... be together a lot this year. Hehe.
Rinko's aspirations are to... love you more than last year.
Is it the end of the month already... Hey, what's the funniest thing you've done lately？
I think for Rinko is... a limited spring edition potato chip. I look forward to them every year.
For Rinko... it has to be flower viewing, I'm a fan. I like cherry blossoms.
For Rinko... it has to be taking a casual walk, I think. A walk in spring makes me happy.
For Rinko... I guess it's summer, and the fact that we went to the beach. Too standard？
For Rinko... shaved ice. If you don't eat it, it doesn't feel like summer.
For Rinko... fireworks. Big fireworks shows are nice, but fireworks sold at convenience stores are hard to ignore.
For Rinko... reading, I guess. Autumn for reading, of course.
For Rinko... cooking, I guess. Not that it's the autumn of appetite, but I'm getting into the swing of things.
For Rinko... bargains, I guess. Even if I don't buy anything, it's fun just to look at them.
For Rinko... skiing, after all. I want to ski all year round.
For Rinko... maybe a hot pot. It's fun to sit around a pot with family, isn't it？
For Rinko... I guess snow. I'm just going to curl up in the kotatsu, though.
Hey, do you have time right now？ If you're free, play with me.
What are you doing now？ I'm going to let off some steam.
Hey. If you're free, let's play.
So, was it fun？ Do you want to do it again？
You're in for a treat... Well, okay.
Hey. What shall we do for fun？
Do you want to play Puzzle- Dama？
Do you want to play TwinBee？
Want to try play Yie Ar Kung Fu with Rinko？
We're not going to do it. Then, I'll see you next time.
Let's play "Just Count". Rinko will measure 30 seconds on the clock, you count 30 seconds in your head, and when the time is up, say "Stop" when the time is up.
Too bad. It hasn't been 30 seconds yet.
Almost！ Too bad, you were so close.
Too bad you're too late. You have to say "stop".
